snippet.title: Space Invaders Extreme Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Space Invaders Extreme now! http://store.steampowered.com/app/744050

The critically acclaimed update to the Space Invaders franchise has arrived to invade Steam with greatly improved graphics and audio! Packed with pulsing, vibrant visuals enhanced further by interactive sound.
Sign up for more news here: https://www.taito.com/steam
